highlights.text: Saran has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “รออยู่อย่างนั้น” is the highest at #49.
“ยิ้มลา (jasmine)” by BOWKYLION is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #188.
“ไฟเย็น” by YOUNGOHM has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 959 days straight.
“ไกล” by Musketeers is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 62 spots at #106.
